{"tid":2110901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 李嘉欣劉海髮型 被連登網民嘲「老少女」","createTime":"2020-07-16T08:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T09:19:12.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f16d2abc1f07fdda86804120fb6d0895fce2852","tid":2110901,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mo70Uk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMo70Uk6.jpg&h=000ca001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">李嘉欣近日以劉海造型亮相。</span><br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣日前在微博分享自拍和粉絲道晚安，還在評論區補充「睡前跟大家說聲晚安」。自拍中，李嘉欣以空氣齊劉海出鏡，已經50歲的她皮膚依然緊緻，不過連登網民對這個造型卻有不同評論，「這個劉海造型不適合美人啊」「這張有點顯老」「貌似氣質女神不適合這髮型」。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣罕見曬自拍，大家都在為她的不老容顏感嘆，殊不知她不是曬漂亮的臉蛋而是秀新髮型，50歲李嘉欣剪掉多年偏分的髮型意外減齡。<br />\n<br />\n但也有連登網友認為，李嘉欣剪了空氣劉海像個「老少女」，50歲貴婦氣質都剪沒了！"},{"pid":"82c378d66a3d15cae0d03926d3715d87b352cd19","tid":2110901,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafa982e17d3a101be413a6e13c121cb32c5a8f5","tid":2110901,"uid":84588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"巨型顴骨再加尖長下巴好似dodo jer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f384b7772a31c4f6a505c822bae94b6a75669b","tid":2110901,"uid":362900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"個咀大撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9040175636700d16c246c2d724565e20154ab6","tid":2110901,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:39:38.000Z","msg":"前幾日maymay 咪開咗 old news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596dc942630eaf65b21b6cfe3b4c261e5fd0cd3b","tid":2110901,"uid":41863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"你捧個西女